Reasoning: The paper presents an AI system for generating narrative arcs and collaborating with human storytellers, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the system architecture and design choices, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper includes a case-study usage of the system and presents metrics for evaluating human-machine creative generation, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
